</div>

<div class="Offer " style="padding-bottom: 15vh;">
    <h1 class="col-md-12 col-xs-12 Center">What We Offer</h1>
    <div class="col-md-2"></div>
    <div class="col-md-3">
        <div class="card" style="width: 18rem;">
            <img class="card-img-top Center" src="images/server1.webp" alt="Card image cap">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title Center"><b>Dedicated Servers</b></h5><br>
                <p class="card-text">Having a bad connection to a game?  Our servers provide a 1 Gbps internet connection to a dedicated server.</p>

            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-3">
        <div class="card" style="width: 18rem;">
            <img class="card-img-top Center" src="images/server2.webp" alt="Card image cap">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title Center"><b>Persistent System</b></h5><br>
                <p class="card-text">Our Persistent System allows you to play on all your favorite tables without having to start over. You can use the same save no matter who is hosting.</p>

            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="col-md-3">
        <div class="card" style="width: 18rem;">
            <img class="card-img-top Center" src="images/GrandPappyPoker_Background-960w.webp" alt="Card image cap">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title Center"><b>Welcoming Community</b></h5><br>
                <p class="card-text">Because of our constant growth you will never have to search for people to play with. You will always have a great group of people ready and willing to have a fun time.</p>

            </div>
        </div>

    </div>
    <div class="col-md-2"></div>
    <div class="spacer"></div>
    <div class="spacer"></div>
</div>



